## ─── velo-web .env ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser.
## See docs/LOCAL_SETUP.md §4 for acquisition recipes.

# Vite dev server port. vite.config.ts throws at boot if unset.
PORT=5173

# Vite base path. vite.config.ts throws at boot if unset. Use "/" for local dev.
BASE_PATH=/

# Free at https://cloud.reown.com → New Project → copy Project ID
# Without it the wallet picker shows "Invalid project ID"
VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=
